&gt;&gt;     be aware of is that the shouldProcessRule can be used to limit
&gt;&gt;     the umbra treatment to the urls of your choice.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;     &lt;bean id=&quot;amqpUrlReceiver&quot;
&gt;&gt;     class=&quot;org.archive.crawler.frontier.AMQPUrlReceiver&quot;&gt;
&gt;&gt;         &lt;property name=&quot;queueName&quot;
&gt;&gt;     value=&quot;archiveit.prod.9876-20150704232858960&quot;/&gt;
